  "title": "Ai'kani's Knighting Ceremony",
  "summary": "In the candlelit courtyard of the cruiser Refrain of Anshalar, the secretly gathered Jedi Order convenes for a solemn dual ceremony presided over by Luke Skywalker. Padawan Ai'kani Za'netra and the Sullustan initiate Ikihsa Enb'Zik wait in the meditation chamber before being summoned forth. Surrounded by a circle of ignited lightsabers held in respect, Ai'kani kneels and is dubbed a Jedi Knight of the Republic by Luke. Luke then calls Enb'Zik forward and, after probing the true desire of his heart, accepts his oath and bestows on him the rank of Jedi Apprentice. The gathering erupts in applause, and as the solemnity breaks, Ai'kani welcomes Enb'Zik as a brother while his Horansi wife Snarl bounds in to embrace him.",
